section.para:
			Quarter Sessions may enlarge Highways; 
Damages to Owners to be assessed by a Jury,; not exceeding 25 Years Purchase; On Payment of Money, Owner divested of his Interest in the Ground; 
Assessments to be levied on Inhabitants for repairing the Roads, and purchasing Land for enlarging Highways, &c.; if not paid within 10 Days, Distress.
